{"tid":598110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好討厭每次發佈係重要嘅時候就起咗身","createTime":"2018-03-19T08:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T16:43:14.000Z","uid":88489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"397fe77f88076cf17186adc2d3bd83a8d0ae7649","tid":598110,"uid":88489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"有一次我發夢見到我表弟比蛇食咗落肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係只係得我可以救翻佢，然而佢阿媽係隔離係咁叫我。等我就快救到佢嘅時候就夢醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有一次就係發夢見到同班嘅男仔，平日係冇乜傾計果啲黎。係中學嘅班房裏面佢同我講：我想同你講啲嘢！但係我同佢係大學同學嚟嘅，嗰陣時覺得好真實完全冇咩問題。之後我突然就比鬧鐘嘈左起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗住發翻夢睇下下文如何，佢同我講啲乜嘢啦，但係最後都徒勞無功<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地又有冇啲咩有趣嘅夢又係發到一半就起咗身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e9729b8d4b73bdc4ca909aa9cc02b6222ee754","tid":598110,"uid":88489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:30:09.000Z","msg":"冇人回，自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98dfc6286bef85dbfcd280e92e47cbd2b2be7044","tid":598110,"uid":88489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:30:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18a2656ccc057bddd296ae363d9fa11a0fd9258c","tid":598110,"uid":88489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:30:47.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686d2c2f68e80b06ab5fb70a163f101f334b0370